This project focuses on analyzing sales performance using Power BI, providing key insights into product sales, sales personnel efficiency, and customer purchasing trends.

Imported and cleaned sales data for accurate visualization.
Created interactive dashboards to track sales performance.
Analyzed sales trends across products, salespersons, and customers.
Identified key revenue-driving products and high-performing sales representatives.
Technology Stack: Power BI, DAX, SQL, Data Visualization.

Outcome:
Improved decision-making through data-driven insights.
Enhanced sales strategy by identifying top-performing products and sales trends.
Provided a dynamic and interactive dashboard for real-time monitoring.
